## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **tasimelteon (Hetlioz) 2014** = first FDA non-24 sleep-wake disorder (totally blind 환자). MT1/MT2 selective. 시장 narrow — totally blind 인구 한정. 2020 Hetlioz LQ = first FDA Smith-Magenis Syndrome (SMS) 16세 이상 확장. quantum-VQE 의 MT1/MT2 selectivity fit primary path.
2. **ramelteon (Rozerem) 2005** = first FDA MT1/MT2 selective insomnia. classical BZD/Z-drug 대안. tasimelteon precursor.
3. **agomelatine (Valdoxan)** = MT1/MT2 + 5-HT2C antagonist (EU/JP, US 미승인). MDD 적응증 + chronotype 변동. tri-target 약리 paradigm.
4. **melatonin OTC supplement** = FDA 미규제 supplement (US), Europe/JP 의약품 — 규제 dichotomy. prolonged-release Circadin EU 2007 = 인지 + 수면 노인 (≥55세). dose 0.3-3mg variability + 임상 evidence 한정.
5. **lemborexant + daridorexant + suvorexant DORA 2014-2022** = orexin receptor antagonist insomnia paradigm shift. cross-sleep distinct. quantum-VQE 의 OX1R/OX2R selectivity fit.
6. **modafinil + armodafinil 1998/2007** = narcolepsy + 교대근무 sleep + jet lag (off-label). dopamine + histamine wake-promoting. dopamine non-amphetamine paradigm.
7. **bright light therapy 10,000 lux 30 min morning** = SAD + DSPS — device-not-drug, FDA device class II. non-pharmacologic chronotherapy 1차.
8. **circadian cancer chemo (Levi 1997 + EORTC)** = 5-FU 24시간 modulated infusion — colorectal. chronoradiotherapy = research (Mansfield 2024 small-N HNSCC). 임상 evidence 한정 + adoption 낮음.
9. **clock-gene downstream 약리** = BMAL1 + CLOCK + PER1/2/3 + CRY1/2 + Rev-erbα + Rorα/β/γ — research only. KL001 (CRY) + SR9009/SR9011 (Rev-erbα) + PF-670462 (CK1δ/ε) = chemical biology tool, not approved drug. quantum-VQE 의 PPI scaffold fit research-grade only.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, chronotherapy 임상 의미 한정. 시장 = tasimelteon Hetlioz 2014/2020 narrow indication + ramelteon mature + DORA 신규 + cancer chronotherapy paradigm 미정착 + bright light therapy device-not-drug + melatonin OTC supplement 규제 dichotomy 미국 vs EU/JP + clock-gene downstream 약리 paradigm research-only.

